title: Funky & FABULOUS__Private Pool__Guest House__WALK 2 Springs__W/D Incl
posting_body: Stunning Mid Century Modern home in the heart of Zilker!
This home features 4 bedrooms/2 bathrooms with a separate 1/1 guest house
Not to mention, a pool with a magnificent view of Barton Springs/Zilker Park/West Lake Hills
Recently extensively renovated with an eye toward preserving the mid-century aesthetic
Recent upgrades include: new kitchen cabinets, countertops, and appliances
A wall of floor-to-ceiling windows in the living room that open fully to the outside
Recently built out office and laundry room with an ice machine for endless soft ice
Wood flooring throughout home aside from Terrazzo floors in living room
Recent master bathroom renovation with new tile, custom vanities, new bathtub and toilet
Completely renovated backyard: resurfaced swimming pool and looks out over Barton Springs pool and is situated to capture the sunsets on the hilltop
Situated in one of the best locations within the Zilker neighborhood at the footstep of Downtown, walk into Zilker Park or bike around the greater 78704 with ease
